# Keyboard configuration
# nbsp:level3n - AltGr + Space -> non breakable space
#                AltGr + Shift + Space -> thin non breakable space
# compose:menu - Use Menu as compose key
# caps:hyke    - makes CapsLock an additional WINDOWS key
